org.linqs.psl.reasoner

Class ExecutableReasoner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.reasoner.Reasoner
      • org.linqs.psl.reasoner.ExecutableReasoner

  • public abstract class ExecutableReasoner
extends Reasoner
    An abstract superclass for reasoners implemented as command-line executables. Ground models are provided to the executable and results are read via temporary files.
